<div class='container'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-md-8'>
      <h1 class='page-header'>Become a Messenger</h1>

<p>
  Thank you for your interest in becoming a Messenger. We are excited that you want to support the Muses and their projects, joining a community of Messengers from around the world who believe in and support the power of music.
</p>

<p>
  By becoming a Messenger, you have a chance to get to know the Muses you choose to support.  Upon acceptance, Muses are asked to provide correspondence letters/emails with their Messengers through the duration of the project, allowing you to connect directly with the Muses you support and making this more than a digital transaction. Muses are also asked to provide a final performance video or music file to you and the Messengers who support them. That way, you understand exactly how your support has transformed the Muses lives.
</p>

<%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => registration_url(resource_name), :html => {:class => 'form-horizontal', :id => 'donor_regis', :role => 'form'}) do |f| %>
        <%= devise_error_messages! %>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :profile_picture, 'Profile Picture', :class => 'col-sm-2 control-label'%>
          <div class='col-sm-10'>
            <%= f.file_field :profile_picture, :required => '' %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :firstname, 'First Name', :class => 'col-sm-2 control-label'%>
          <div class='col-sm-10'>
            <%= f.text_field :firstname, :class => 'form-control', :required => '' %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :lastname, 'Last Name', :class => 'col-sm-2 control-label'%>
          <div class='col-sm-10'>
            <%= f.text_field :lastname, :class => 'form-control', :required => '' %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :email, 'Email', :class => 'col-sm-2 control-label'%>
          <div class='col-sm-10'>
            <%= f.email_field :email, :class => 'form-control', :required => '' %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :password, :class => 'col-sm-2 control-label'%>
          <div class='col-sm-10'>
            <%= f.password_field :password, :class => 'form-control', :required => ''%>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :password_confirmation, :class => 'col-sm-2 control-label'%>
          <div class='col-sm-10'>
            <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, :class => 'form-control', :required => ''%>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div><%= f.submit "Sign up", :class => 'btn btn-default btn-success', :onclick => "document.getElementById('donor_regis').submit()" %></div>
      <% end %>

      <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
